Dean CARBAJAL, petitioner,
v.
WELLS FARGO BANK, et al.
No. 16-6268.
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 5, 2016.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Colorado dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
